  "texts": [
    "We used TopAI Tools, foot_16 a renowned search engine indexing more than 11K AI systems and searched for the following relevant terms: \"literature review\", \"systematic review\", \"scientific research\", \"search engine\", and \"writing assistant\".",
    "This search returned 164 tools, which were processed using the same two-stage selection process described in Sect. 3.",
    "We first screened the tools by using their short descriptions and then all authors performed a thorough examination of 18 candidate tools.",
    "This process yielded 11 tools in this domain.",
    "Table 5 reports an overview of these tools."
